{"tid":1718994,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教育局宣布全港學校明日至星期日繼續停課","createTime":"2019-11-14T03:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T04:27:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8cb561c14b13dc65753a2865eafcd6d8aea6605e","tid":1718994,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:42:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492114-20191114.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492114-20191114.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=269bf9cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492114-20191114.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ad97cca6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492114-20191114.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"09413953d44efd3a2a288ddf7e60ca670ce2f95d","tid":1718994,"uid":324246,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:43:59.000Z","msg":"又再次跌入圈套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a77c8442e9129eea70415bfefd1a40a73daada4a","tid":1718994,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:44:42.000Z","msg":"教育局表示，由於堵路及阻礙交通服務情況持續，而且範圍廣泛，基於安全考慮，全港學校，包括幼稚園、小學、中學及特殊學校，明日至星期日繼續停課。<br />\n<br />\n在上課日停課期間，學校須保持校舍開放，教職員在安全可行的情況下須返回學校照顧返抵學校的學生，與家長保持溝通，並在安全可行的情況下方可安排學生返家。<br />\n<br />\n教育局再次強烈呼籲停止一切暴力及破壞行為，盡快令社會回復秩序，讓學童安全上學。學生應留在家中，不要在街上流連，遠離危險，更切勿參加違法活動。<br />\n<br />\n教育局會繼續跟進最新發展，適時為學校提供進一步指引及支援。"},{"pid":"3e6da02efd36f5590f0016776f0ece113220eec0","tid":1718994,"uid":72825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09413953d44efd3a2a288ddf7e60ca670ce2f95d","tid":1718994,"uid":324246,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:43:59.000Z","msg":"又再次跌入圈套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 